# Description

Fix some code style  issues in `StatuePlugin`:
* There are many variables in plugin `StatePlugin` written in lowercase with words separated by underscores. This pr rewrites these in normal C# variable style;
* Add more info when throw Exception;
* More `var` style;
* Unift JObject initialization;

